Grammar

    0 $accept: prog $end

    1 prog: lines

    2 lines: ε
    3      | line NEWLINE lines

    4 line: exprs

    5 exprs: ε
    6      | expr
    7      | expr SPACE exprs

    8 expr: CMD arith_expr
    9     | assignment
   10     | LABEL
   11     | SPECIAL_CMD
   12     | CUSTOM_VAR SPACE arith_expr
   13     | CALL SPACE STRING
   14     | MISC_ID
   15     | fn
   16     | COMMENT
   17     | error

   18 assignment: VAR SET arith_expr
   19           | CMD SET arith_expr
   20           | CUSTOM_VAR SET arith_expr

   21 val: VAR
   22    | INT
   23    | FLOAT

   24 fn: MISC_ID '(' params ')'

   25 params: arith_expr
   26       | MISC_ID
   27       | arith_expr ',' params
   28       | MISC_ID ',' params

   29 arith_expr: val
   30           | fn
   31           | arith_expr '+' arith_expr
   32           | arith_expr '-' arith_expr
   33           | arith_expr '*' arith_expr
   34           | arith_expr '/' arith_expr
   35           | '(' arith_expr ')'
   36           | '-' arith_expr


